  <h1>What is a message queue?</h1>
  <div class="artmeta"><span>By Coldwast</span><span>Updated Jul 9, 2026</span><span>8 min read</span><span class="tag">#messagequeue</span><span class="tag">#architecture</span><span class="tag">#backend</span></div>
  <nav class="toc" id="toc"></nav>
  <figure>
    <img class="hero" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/18631424/pexels-photo-18631424.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200" alt="An automated conveyor belt carrying items through a factory" width="1200" height="420" loading="eager" />
